Frequently Asked Questions Q: What’s the advantage of staying in corporate housing over staying in a hotel? A: Corporate housing units are typically less expensive than hotels, certainly much more spacious and comfortable, and always much more like home with a fully equipped kitchen, relaxing seating areas, and a pleasant work Often you’ll also have a dedicated parking spot for easy access to your Apartment communities in most cases will offer larger gyms, pools, and BBQ grilling Think about the last time you stayed for an extended period of time in a hotel room, then make a mental comparison to the comforts of home you were Q: Are all your units furnished? A: We offer three levels of furniture and housewares packages and can customize to meet your specific Our customer care staff will work with you to make sure your housing meets your Q: What if I need an apartment right now? A: We nearly always have an available unit for hours And if we do not, we have a network of partners to draw Q: Do you provide housekeeping service? A: Yes, if Housekeeping is an additional option, not always We offer options for weekly, and monthly Q: Do you have units equipped for the handicapped? A: A percentage of our available units are equipped with handrails, large doorway openings, and other standard mobility assists for our handicapped Handicapped access will be based on the inventory available at the time of your Q: Are pets allowed in your units? A: Some properties allow We can negotiate that with you when you book with We will match you with a property that approves of your Q: Can you bill my employer or my insurance company? A: Either would require approval from the company being We can also bill an individual We accept all forms of Q: I don’t plan to have a car during my How can you accommodate my needs? A: Each property in our portfolio has a “walkscore.” A property with a walkscore of or higher is considered fairly The higher the score, the more likely you can walk to most When you and our customer care staff discuss your needs, you can let us know your transportation We can recommend your options for transportation from your arriving airport, walking distances from your apartment to restaurants and services, and public transportation We know our communities well and can help you get around Q: Speaking of activities, do you provide a guide to the city? A: Your packet will include a list of the Top Ten activities as well as local eateries that we personally Q: What is the minimum lease term in days? A: Currently the minimum stay is Q: Will I be occupying an apartment, a condominium or a house? A: That’s an excellent question as each has different Work with our customer care staff so that you know exactly what type of unit you are leasing and what’s Currently, the majority of our properties are apartment Please let us know if your need require other headerOffset: footerDepth: sidebarHeight: currentScroll: sidebarMarginTop: Access Corporate Housing Rest ve Got Access Corporate Housing About Us Browse By Location FAQs Contact Us Become a Partner News   About Us – Access Corporate Housing Access Corporate Housing About Us Browse By Location FAQs Contact Us Become a Partner News Toggle navigation Access Corporate Housing About Us Browse By Location FAQs Contact Us Become a Partner News Rest ve Got Call us now! If you encounter any issues submitting over Duosuma, please let us know and send an email submission Blog pitches are open and not hosted on ​ All submissions are read We welcome people of all ages, ethnicities, and sexualities to We are open to multiple and simultaneous submissions as long as you state such in your cover Unless solicited, please submit only previously unpublished work we do not consider work that has been featured on personal websites or social media as ​ All submissions should be in Times New Roman, with poetry Please do not include any identifying information within the body of the work ​ At this time, we are able to offer a modest honorarium to accepted Upon acceptance, EX POST MAGAZINE receives first North American publishing and archival All rights revert back to the author upon We ask that you credit us if the work is reprinted in the ​ ​ EXPEDITED DECISION POLICY We aim to return decisions within a few weeks, but if you wish to receive a decision within three days, attach a receipt of a $3 donation via our PayPal below to an email with your submission to —do not submit via All funds go toward supporting our microgrant and paying ​ ​ YOUNG WRITERS SPOTLIGHT For any of the below genres, feel free to note in your submission if you are a young writer (ages and under) for special inclusion in our issue and ​ POETRY Please send up to five Include a brief biography with your cover We also accept short videos of spoken ​ PROSE Please send up to three works of fiction or nonfiction under 7,000 words Include a brief biography with your cover ​ DRAMA Please send up to two plays under ten pages Include a brief biography with your cover ART Please send up to five pieces of Include a brief biography with your cover letter, as well as an artist statement under words and description of medium We accept photography, digital art, painting, and mixed ​ ESSAYS, INTERVIEWS, REVIEWS, Interested in publishing on our blog? Projects » MedReportGuard About Support Contact Projects California has mandatory reporting laws that require HCP’s to report any victim of DV (Domestic violence) to law enforcement (PC ). The problem for HCP’s is that there is no standardized reporting form, no way to track law enforcement (22 police jurisdictions in Alameda county alone) receipt of the mandated report, no centralized data collection, no mechanism to guarantee victims are followed up and provided support services and, no acknowledgement to the health care provider that the patient has received The DVRR report provides standardized data collection that can be aggregated across regional geographic The MedReportGuard application was developed collaboratively with the district attorney, law enforcement and health care The program was uniquely designed to meet the security requirements for both law enforcement and medical information (HIPAA). It is supported by the Alameda County Medical Center, The Police Chief’s Association, and Alameda County Health Care It is currently being tested in the Emergency Department of Highland Hospital and there are plans to deploy to all Alameda County emergency departments and community clinics as soon initial revisions are About Support Contact Projects   About » MedReportGuard About Support Contact Projects About MedReportGuard, LLC is a creative technology company specializing in custom application services for the healthcare and law enforcement Our applications are used primarily to facilitate the Domestic Violence and Sexual Assault Mandatory and Forensic Reporting We prioritize the security and protection of all ePHI within our In addition, we bring technology forward and user experience solutions for our applications making them easy to use, in a secure About Support Contact Projects   MedReportGuard » Internet based medical reporting forms About Support Contact Projects MedReportGuard develops and maintains internet based medical reporting forms designed for Health Care Providers (HCP) to be used in hospitals and DVRR in Alameda County The MedReportGuard DVRR application was developed collaboratively with the Alameda County District Attorney, law enforcement and health care MedReportGuard is committed to developing creative technology solutions that address data reporting About Us About Support Contact Projects   Contact » MedReportGuard About Support Contact Projects Contact Your Name (required) Your Email (required) Subject Your Message About Support Contact Projects   Knowledge Base » MedReportGuard About Support Contact Projects Knowledge Base DVRR DVRR Quick Overview View all 1 article SART e923 Power Off Device Creating Custom Fields Creating User Accounts for Individuals Creating User Accounts for Team Leaders How To Clear Cache View all 5 articles About Support Contact Projects

At Schwed Pediatric Dentistry, we believe that tooth decay is not an inevitable part of With proper education and a concerted effort, children can grow up with a healthy mouth and may never require surgical treatment for tooth Checkups and Dental Cleanings Just as you wouldn’t miss a visit with your pediatrician, the and cleaning as recommended by the American Academy of Pediatric Dentistry is essential to ensuring your child’s oral health and proper And since it’s easier to treat a small issue than a big one, it’s essential to detect problems as soon as they Often, a prescription toothpaste and some dietary changes are all that is required to stop a new cavity from developing! Fluoride Treatments and Dental Sealants Fluoride is a natural compound that has been proven to strengthen tooth enamel, which is the first defense against Fluoride gel, foam, or varnish is applied to the teeth for a few moments, but the benefits are long Dental sealants are made of a clear protective coating that is painted into the grooves on the biting surface of children’s Once dried, sealants act as a protective barrier between the teeth and harmful Digital Sometimes dental problems begin where they cannot be seen, such as on the surfaces between two The standard of care for detecting cavities is through periodic digital The procedure is completely safe, and because the are digital, Schwed can share the results with you immediately on the computer Sports Mouthguards Do you have a budding athlete in the family? In that case, a sports mouthguard is a Made of smooth, comfortable plastic, a sports mouthguard protects teeth, lips, gums and tongue from Schwed takes a mold of your child’s mouth to create a customized sports mouthguard for him or her to wear during play or Sedation We understand that going to the dentist can cause some young patients to feel But while some children only experience a very small amount of anxiety, others have more serious needs that can only be addressed with sedation Nitrous oxide , also known as ‘laughing gas,’ is a gas that is delivered along with oxygen through a nose mask during treatment and provides mild The body clears it within a few moments of turning it off, with no lasting negative Oral conscious sedation is a liquid medication that Schwed administers in the office about 1 hour prior to commencing Your child will be relaxed and even a little Schwed reserves oral conscious sedation as a great option when nitrous oxide is not quite enough to help your child remain relaxed through General anesthesia , which is administered in our office by a trained anesthesiologist, is reserved for lengthy and involved appointments or for children with a medical condition that prevents them from sitting in the dentist’s chair for too Restorative Dentistry For those times when your children’s smiles need care to restore the appearance or function of a tooth, Schwed offers restorative dental Fillings If your child has a small cavity or slightly damaged tooth, we no longer have to repair it with a dark gray metal Now, we can use a composite resin material to their enamel to seamlessly restore any compromised dental fillings also help support the remaining tooth much better than traditional fillings, meaning you can trust a repaired tooth to last for many years to Plus, they only take one brief appointment to Solea Laser Schwed is proud to offer laser dentistry with Solea®, a , CO2 laser system that is for both hard and soft tissue dental Because treatment with Solea is so comfortable and virtually , most patients do not require any That means there are no needles, no drills, and no lingering sensation of numbness after a procedure is In fact, Solea is so efficient that should we discover a cavity during one of your child’s routine dental checkups, you may not require an additional Schwed

So HOW does Bredemarket do these things? Evolution University supports changemakers across the full entrepreneurial lifecycle from connecting to a purpose, evaluating ideas, launching and growing, to accelerator and pitch Courses are relevant to any organization where empathy, entrepreneurial and strategic thinking skills are valued, including for purpose orgs, established businesses, individual entrepreneurs and Do I need to have a firm "idea" to take the Mini MBA for Changemakers? As the saying goes, luck is what happens when preparation meets EU courses allow you to work with identified products and services or experiment with ideas while developing key competencies, readying you to lead or join a Consider the United Nations Sustainability Development Goals and imagine a way to help solve one of these problems and transform our Looking for ideas to reduce global warming? DrawDown has done extensive research to determine the top solutions and corresponding See their Climate Solutions to find out Another option is to look at NASA s Technology Transfer Program with hundreds of technologies for entrepreneurs to Check out the possibilities and imagine a way to bring one You might end up with a great idea after all! EU courses are available to anyone who is ready to make a positive Starting and growing programs and enterprises takes passion and perseverance so come ready to give it your best What is a changemaker? Changemaker is a word coined by and a movement to inspire people to shift from purely profit driven enterprises to ones that make positive change for people and the EU believes it is the only way to create a sustainable Is Evolution University an accredited college? EU is the way of the future where people gain diverse skills with shorter certifications that improve competencies and increase contribution EU is not a traditional Are EU courses accredited? All courses are built at the quality level for continuing education and college In the future as EU grows, we may be able to offer these Today, each course provides a certificate of completion, which can be framed and shared digitally on LinkedIn, Twitter and Facebook and more . Why do I need to take the MORE compassion course? As we move further into the information era, the skills that differentiate humans from machines are compassion and EU believes compassion and empathy are essential skills for making our world a better place and offers this course free to everyone as part of our spirit of What type of technology do I need to take EU courses? Courses and webinars are accessible on any internet connected device such as computers, tablets, or smart Although its personal preference, a laptop or desktop computer is usually a better environment to complete more involved assignments as in the Mini MBA versus a smart What is social learning? Many online courses are on demand only, where you move through the course by yourself watching videos, reading, and Social learning provides a higher level of learning by blending , group interaction, and instructor The science behind social learning proves it is the most effective method for developing more complex skills and results in higher completion Whereas technology provides greater access to education, it cannot replace the social connection humans innately Does EU offer customized courses for specific groups? Am I spending time with TV or my phone minutes prior to bed? This keeps your brain in a state of Bedtime rituals are the new Replace this screen time with reading, journaling, a bath shower or some quality time with your partner or When was the last time I tried going to bed earlier? What’s an incremental goal I’ve been thinking about that I can partner and associate with getting out of bed, that’ll motivate me? How Mira Works - Mira Security +1 (412) Home How Mira Works About Mira Events Contact Select Page Orchestrate Encrypted Traffic Across the Enterprise Using Safe, Secure and Scalable How Mira Works Mira Encrypted Traffic Orchestration (ETO) automatically detects SSL, TLS and SSH traffic and feeds it to one or more security tools that detect and mitigate any threats that may be No special interfaces or software changes are required to the security They simply receive traffic from Mira ETO as if it was traffic directly from the This means the existing security stacks can regain their effectiveness, diminished by the increase in encrypted traffic, simply by deploying Mira ETO to feed MIRA DEPLOYMENT MODES Software Subscription License Mira ETO software is licensed as a subscription Subscriptions can be for months or months and can be upgraded during the subscription The license purchased determines the amount of encrypted traffic that can be decrypted to provide visibility for security Mira ETO Demo In this video we see how Mira Security Encrypted Traffic Orchestration can enable your network security systems to properly monitor traffic and detect threats that they would otherwise miss due to DEMO Enterprises need to balance security risks of not decrypting traffic with the privacy implications of doing Mira ETO provides the flexible policy controls to ensure that balance is Flexible policy control features of Mira ETO enable enterprises to enforce policy on what encryption mechanisms are allowed in order to ensure a secure For encrypted traffic that is allowed, there are policies that enable control over which encrypted flows are decrypted and made visible to security Policy controls can optionally make use of the Mira category database and or a locally created category database to determine which types of traffic are Mira ETO software is designed for decryption and can work with link speeds of 1, , , and soon Gbps, providing decryption for anywhere from <1 Gbps of encrypted traffic up to 100 Mira’s ETO software supports high rates of new TLS handshakes per second, ensuring that there is no performance impact when The software is architected to allow the use of external hardware PKI engines enabling both decryption performance and new handshake performance to be scaled even Appliance Licensing A license can be used on either a virtual appliance or on one of the hardware appliances available from Mira The following matrix shows which licenses can be used on specific appliance models: Virtual Appliance Details: Support for KVM and Licensed capacity defines requirements for virtual appliance in terms of memory and CPU LOOK DEEPER INTO MIRA Mira removes enterprise network “blind spots” by providing visibility into This may make for a strong TV and movie trope, the sense of mystery that surrounds the unknown for the However, what would “going off the grid” actually entail in the current digital age? Sure, years ago going off grid was a piece of cake, Move to a different city and don’t call people from your past life: the Nowadays, though, you’d need to be born and have fanatically maintained insulation from the tentacles of the data collection machine, avoiding data brokers and people search websites scraping information around the The Advent of Data Brokers in Mass Public Data Collection Data brokers consistently search for your digital They collect and save every scrap they can find, and compile this into common profiles, selling your information to anyone willing to buy it for their people search Your teachers were right, your permanent record is But where does this data come from? That’s the most shocking part: it comes from Every transaction you make, every new step in your digital footprint, adds yet another piece to a constantly growing puzzle that is your digital Does this bother you? That’s where services such as Removaly Defender come See more about our service offerings . Where Do Data Brokers Get Your Data? The easiest method for data brokers to gather your information is from when you willingly hand over your data to third Signing up for store loyalty accounts or discount cards? Congratulations, your data is being stored and When you make shopping trips, your purchase history goes into databanks and are tracked, sold, and traded by data brokers around the Example: Grocery Stores But why do grocery stores need your data? The answer is simple: to make market decisions with everything from advertising to inventory to the psychology of This data can help to monitor how quickly broccoli sells, when to lower the price, and when to move it to a different part of the produce However, it also provides data brokers with deep pockets information about your purchasing habits, whether it be chicken soup, tissues, ginger ale, or ice Ever wonder how that ad for cold medicine randomly decides to show up in your daily life? How do Personas make my Sales team more effective? How do Personas make my Product Development more effective? FYI What is a Persona? A persona is a way of representing complex customer and market data in a way that a human can actually understand and Think of a persona as a fictional character or and Personas have various more specific names that refer to how the persona is used for a specific business Marketing teams may refer to a Buyer or Customer Sales teams sometimes call them Prospect Product development teams may refer to a User In all cases, market and or customer data is used to identify the ideal characteristics of the people (personas) your company Usually elements like demographics, and decision criteria are identified and At their best, personas are dynamic entities who are updated as your understanding of your customers A persona has all the elements of a “real” person who buys or uses your product or This includes elements of a life story and personal This helps everyone in your organization relate to your persona in a personal, connected Negative personas are an incredibly useful and underutilized business who waste your sales and marketing teams efforts can be identified and eliminated from your sales cycle Your product development team can use negative personas to help them make it more difficult for “problem users” to misuse your Here at Persona fx , we believe that specificity is an essential characteristic of your Other organizations may encourage you to use ranges when describing your persona’s age, income or level of We think that’s a The whole purpose of a persona is to help your team relate to your prospects and customers as And individuals do not have a range of We’ve also discovered that when we are specific, we often uncover specific decision criteria that would have been less obvious if we were looking at a group in For example, our year old founder has different preferences for communication and makes buying decisions differently than our year old, even though they share many other Personas with different responsibilities can often find value in your product, even as they use it How is a Persona different from a Market Segment? A market segment describes a group of people in your market while a Persona distills the essentials of a market segment into just one While a market segment is described generally, a Persona is It’s the difference between “23-27 year old women with degrees in computer science” and your sister, Jessica or your fiance, What difference can Persona fx ’s Personas make in my business? One of the most common mistakes businesses make is confusing our customers with ourselves, confusing our preferences, pain points and goals with those of our prospects, customers or Persona fx personas uniquely engage your entire team in persona development so everyone can understand and develop empathy for the individuals your business wants to This enables them to make intuitive connections that often aren’t obvious in data Personas used for different purposes emphasize different Your product development team may be more interested in a persona’s goals and online preferences and Your marketing team may be more concerned with where and when to deliver content and your sales team will want most to know how to motivate a prospect to make a buying But everyone in your organization should at least know what your ideal customers want and what beliefs are associated with their Personas also help your team by limiting the potential variables they have to consider, while highlighting the important Using personas, copy writers create more compelling marketing Social media managers make more useful Sales associates have more effective Developers integrate more valuable And because everyone is clear about who is being served, a virtuous cycle is created, making it easier to attract and serve more customers who are ideal for your For this reason, Persona fx recommends that your entire team contributes to the persona development This enables you to access the combined wisdom of various specialists and develop personas who are dimensional and engender real This helps your entire organization relate personally to your prospects and customers and bond in common It also creates a language that eases communication between your various business A quick google search reveals that applications from Hubspot to Salesforce to GitLab all recommend that you use Why? Stay Informed - Fair Pay Workplace Skip to content Partners Certification Methodology News Stay Informed Stay Informed Sign up to receive updates from the Fair Pay Workplace Initiative and learn how your organization can take the right pay equity Stay Informed Full name Organization name Email If you are human, leave this field Submit Stay In Touch Sign up to receive updates about the Fair Pay Workplace Initiative and Certification Stay Informed Footer Email If you are human, leave this field Submit Connect #WhereFairPayWorks #EqualPayToday For general questions please email us at: Privacy Policy Privacy Policy Fair Pay Workplace © All Rights Site by Smack Happy Design Connect #WhereFairPayWorks #EqualPayToday For general questions please email us at:   Fair Pay Workplace - Pay Equity Certification Skip to content Partners Certification Methodology News Stay Informed Certification The transparent and trusted standard to differentiate organizations dedicated to true pay Get Certified Our Mission To dismantle unlawful pay disparities based on gender, race and ethnicity to create sustained fair pay in the How do I get my company certified? Assessment Standards & Rules for Fair Pay Certification Companies are measured against a set of standards and rules defined by a group of leading experts from corporations, academia, human resources, and the legal These guidelines lay the foundation for a transparent and trusted criteria assessment based on the endorsed methodology of the Fair Pay Workplace to certify an Certification Standards and Rules Independent Certifying Organization Trained certifying agents evaluate work performed and planned related to assessments and ensure a completely unbiased and uniform certification process as well as ongoing The Fair Pay Workplace Alliance is working with GEN (Gender Equity Now) in providing certifying GEN is a national organization focused on helping foster sustainable equity for all Certifying agents have expertise and background in statistics, labor economics, pay equity laws and regulations as well as comp and benefits Certification Certified Fair Pay Workplace Organizations will be provided with tools to promote themselves as a Certified Fair Pay Workplace upon earning the certification and on a timed schedule to maintain their Fair Pay Workplace FAQ What is the Fair Pay Workplace certification? The Fair Pay Workplace certification recognizes organizations dedicated to true pay equity using a transparent and standardized methodology to measure compensation comparisons across gender, race and The methodology in place is developed by experts and offers the decisive measures necessary to enable real progress towards fair pay in today’s What is the Fair Pay Workplace certification working to solve? Not all methodologies used to claim pay equity are created Without one standard of measurement, companies can boast fair pay with a simple pledge or adoption of a methodology that leads to a less than fair Fair Pay Workplace is working to standardize the methodology used and add transparency to an organization’s pay equity Do I need to show proof of having achieved pay equity based on the rules & standards before getting certified? We recognize that it may take time for organizations to reach true equal The certification intends to lead organizations on the right path and create accountability along the Certification does not mean that an organization has necessarily completed remediating rather it means that an organization is committing to adopting the appropriate standards for review, and is agreeing to be subject to ongoing review by the independent certifying Can global employers receive certification? Yes, organizations with employees in multiple countries can receive The “Pay Equity Review” allows global employers to group and compare compensation from employees based on their country of Are employers obligated to take any external actions upon receiving certification? Organizations will be provided with a trusted mark and tools to promote themselves as a Certified Fair Pay How will people know my company is certified? Organizations have an obligation to share a link on their website with an externally facing statement regarding their compliance with Fair Pay Workplace rules and standards, and provide written documentation that demonstrates alignment with the Is the data and planning documentation submitted for the assessment process kept private and confidential? Remediation plans and analyses submitted for assessment are shared under privilege when proper protocols are The methodology and rules & standards applied are transparent but your assessment is kept What is the cost of certification? The assessment fee depends on the total number of employees in the organization and other factors . Please contact Fair Pay Workplace to receive specific details for your Get Certified Stay In Touch Sign up to receive updates about the Fair Pay Workplace Initiative and Certification
